== Demo of Rails 3 with mongoid, cucumber, devise for heroku.

This is not an example of a great application, nor use of cucumber. It is only created to show how to set up a Rails 3 application with mongoid, cucumber and devise to work with heroku and mongohq.

Some comments and details can be read at http://www.naturepreneurship.com/posts/4bfea36c8cbd69794c000003